***whistle.html

<p><a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>From</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Middle_English" class="extiw" title="w:Middle English"><a href = ***wind.html
<head> <meta charset='utf-8'> </head> <body><h1> <a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a> (1221)</h1><br><h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Etymology_1"><a href = vnd.unilang:etymology.html>Etymology</a> 1</span><span class="mw-editsection"></span></h3>
<p><a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>From</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Middle_English" class="extiw" title="w:Middle English"><a href = vnd.unilang:old.html>Old</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:english.html>English</a></a></span> <i class="Latinx mention" lang="ang"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></i> <span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">(</span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">“</span><span class="mention-gloss"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">”</span><span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">)</span>, <a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>from</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Germanic_language" class="extiw" title="w:Proto-Germanic language">Proto-Germanic</a></span> <i class="Latinx mention" lang="gem-pro">*windaz</i>, <a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>from</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Indo-European_language" class="extiw" title="w:Proto-Indo-European language">Proto-Indo-European</a></span> <i class="Latinx mention" lang="ine-pro">*h₂wéh₁n̥tos</i> <span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">(</span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">“</span><span class="mention-gloss"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">”</span><span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">)</span>, <a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>from</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:early.html>earlier</a> <i class="Latinx mention" lang="ine-pro">*h₂wéh₁n̥ts</i> <span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">(</span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">“</span><span class="mention-gloss"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></span><span <div class="sister-wikipedia sister-project noprint floatright" style="border: 1px solid aaa; font-size: 90%; background: f9f9f9; width: 250px; padding: 4px; text-align: left;"><div style="float: left;"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Wikipedia-logo.png/44px-Wikipedia-logo.png" decoding="async" width="44" height="44" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Wikipedia-logo.png/66px-Wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Wikipedia-logo.png/88px-Wikipedia-logo.png 2x" data-file-width="200" data-file-height="200" /></div></div><div style="margin-left: 60px;"><a href = vnd.unilang:english.html>English</a> Wikipedia <a href = vnd.unilang:have.html>has</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:an.html>an</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:article.html>article</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:on.html>on</a>:<div style="margin-left: 10px;"><b class="Latn" lang="en"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beaufort_scale" class="extiw" title="w:Beaufort scale">Beaufort <a href = vnd.unilang:scale.html>scale</a></a></b></div></div><span class="interProject"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beaufort_scale" class="extiw" title="w:Beaufort scale">Wikipedia </a></span></div>

<hr><h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Verb"><a href = vnd.unilang:verb.html>Verb</a></span><span class="mw-editsection"></span></h4>
<p><strong class="Latn headword" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></strong> (<i>third-person <a href = vnd.unilang:singular.html>singular</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:simple.html>simple</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:present.html>present</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en 3 | s | pres-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>winds</a></b>, <i><a href = vnd.unilang:present.html>present</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:participle.html>participle</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en pres | ptcp-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>winding</a></b>, <i><a href = vnd.unilang:simple.html>simple</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:past.html>past</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:and.html>and</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:past.html>past</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:participle.html>participle</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en past | and | past | ptcp-form-of" lang="en">winded</b> <i><a href = vnd.unilang:or.html>or</a></i> <span class="ib-brac qualifier-brac">(</span><span class="ib-content qualifier-content">proscribed</span><span class="ib-brac qualifier-brac">)</span> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en past | and | past | ptcp-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wound</a></b>)
</p>

<p><strong class="Latn headword" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></strong> (<i>third-person <a href = vnd.unilang:singular.html>singular</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:simple.html>simple</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:present.html>present</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en 3 | s | pres-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>winds</a></b>, <i><a href = vnd.unilang:present.html>present</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:participle.html>participle</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en pres | ptcp-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>winding</a></b>, <i><a href = vnd.unilang:simple.html>simple</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:past.html>past</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:and.html>and</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:past.html>past</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:participle.html>participle</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en past | and | past | ptcp-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wound</a></b> <i><a href = vnd.unilang:or.html>or</a></i> <span class="ib-brac qualifier-brac">(</span><span class="ib-content qualifier-content"><a href = vnd.unilang:archaic.html>archaic</a></span><span class="ib-brac qualifier-brac">)</span> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en past | and | past | ptcp-form-of" lang="en">winded</b>)
</p>

<p><strong class="Latn headword" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></strong> (<i><a href = vnd.unilang:plural.html>plural</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en p-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>winds</a></b>)

<h3><span id=".D0.9C.D0.BE.D1.80.D1.84.D0.BE.D0.BB.D0.BE.D0.B3.D0.B8.D1.87.D0.B5.D1.81.D0.BA.D0.B8.D0.B5_.D0.B8_.D1.81.D0.B8.D0.BD.D1.82.D0.B0.D0.BA.D1.81.D0.B8.D1.87.D0.B5.D1.81.D0.BA.D0.B8.D0.B5_.D1.81.D0.B2.D0.BE.D0.B9.D1.81.D1.82.D0.B2.D0.B0"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Морфологические_и_синтаксические_свойства"></span></h3>
<p><b></b>
</p><p><a href = vnd.unilang:существительное.html>Существи́тельное</a>.
<b><a href = vnd.unilang:wind.html>wind</a></b>
</p><p><a href = vnd.unilang:корень.html>Ко́рень</a>: <b>-wind-</b>.

<hr><hr><h4><span id=".D0.97.D0.BD.D0.B0.D1.87.D0.B5.D0.BD.D0.B8.D0.B5"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Значение"><a href = vnd.unilang:значение.html>Значе́ние</a></span></h4>

***wit.html

<p><a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>From</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Middle_English" class="extiw" title="w:Middle English"><a href = class="Latinx mention" lang="ang">witan</i>, <a href = vnd.unilang:from.html>from</a> <span class="etyl"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Germanic_language" class="extiw" lang="ine-pro">*weyd-</i> <span class="mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren">(</span><span class="mention-gloss-double-quote">“</span><span class="mention-gloss"><a href = <hr><h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Noun"><a href = vnd.unilang:noun.html>Noun</a></span><span class="mw-editsection"></span></h4>
<p><strong class="Latn headword" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yard</a></strong> (<i><a href = vnd.unilang:plural.html>plural</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en p-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yards</a></b>)
</p>
<ol><li><a href = vnd.unilang:a.html>A</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:small.html>small</a>, usually uncultivated <a href = vnd.unilang:area.html>area</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:adjoining.html>adjoining</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:or.html>or</a> (<a href = vnd.unilang:now.html>now</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:especially.html>especially</a>) <a href = vnd.unilang:within.html>withiń</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> precincts <a href = vnd.unilang:of.html>of</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:a.html>a</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:house.html>house</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:or.html>or</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:other.html>other</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:build.html>building</a>.
<ul><li><div class="citation-whole"><span class="cited-source"><b>1913</b>,  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_C._Lincoln" class="extiw" title="wikipedia:Joseph C. Lincoln"><a href = vnd.unilang:joseph.html>Joseph</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:c.html>C</a>. <a href = vnd.unilang:lincoln.html>Lincoln</a></a>,  <a href = vnd.unilang:chapter.html>chapter</a> 1, <a href = vnd.unilang:in.html>in</a>  <cite><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://openlibrary.org/works/OL5535161W"><a href = vnd.unilang:mr.html>Mr</a>. Pratt'<a href = vnd.unilang:s.html>s</a> Patients</a></cite>:</span><dl><dd><div class="h-quotation"><span class="Latn e-quotation" lang="en">'Twas <a href = vnd.unilang:early.html>early</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:june.html>June</a>, <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:new.html>new</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:grass.html>grass</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:be.html>was</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:flourish.html>flourishing</a> everywheres, <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> posies <a href = vnd.unilang:in.html>in</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <b><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yard</a></b>—peonies <a href = vnd.unilang:and.html>and</a> such—in <a href = vnd.unilang:full.html>full</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:bloom.html>bloom</a>, <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:sun.html>sun</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:be.html>was</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:shine.html>shining</a>, <a href = vnd.unilang:and.html>and</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:water.html>water</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:of.html>of</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:bay.html>bay</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:be.html>was</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:blue.html>blue</a>, <a href = vnd.unilang:with.html>with</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:light.html>light</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:green.html>green</a> streaks <a href = vnd.unilang:where.html>where</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:shoal.html>shoal</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:show.html>showed</a>.</span></div></dd></dl></div></li></ul></li>

<hr><h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Noun_2"><a href = vnd.unilang:noun.html>Noun</a></span><span class="mw-editsection"></span></h4>
<p><strong class="Latn headword" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yard</a></strong> (<i><a href = vnd.unilang:plural.html>plural</a></i> <b class="Latn form-of lang-en p-form-of" lang="en"><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yards</a></b>)
</p>
<ol><li><a href = vnd.unilang:a.html>A</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:unit.html>unit</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:of.html>of</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:length.html>length</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:equal.html>equal</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:to.html>to</a> 3 <a href = vnd.unilang:foot.html>feet</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:in.html>in</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:the.html>the</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:us.html>Us</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:customary.html>customary</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:and.html>and</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:british.html>British</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:imperial.html>imperial</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:system.html>systems</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:of.html>of</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:measurement.html>measurement</a>, <a href = vnd.unilang:equal.html>equal</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:to.html>to</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:precisely.html>precisely</a> 0.9144 m <a href = vnd.unilang:since.html>since</a> 1959 (<a href = vnd.unilang:us.html>Us</a>) <a href = vnd.unilang:or.html>or</a> 1963 (UK).
<ul><li><div class="citation-whole"><span class="cited-source"><b>1913</b>,  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_C._Lincoln" class="extiw" title="wikipedia:Joseph C. <p><b><a href = vnd.unilang:yard.html>yard</a></b>
</p><p><a href = vnd.unilang:существительное.html>Существи́тельное</a>.

<head> <meta charset='utf-8'> </head> <body><h1> <a href = vnd.unilang:you.html>you</a> (17)</h1><br><h3><span id=".D0.9C.D0.BE.D1.80.D1.84.D0.BE.D0.BB.D0.BE.D0.B3.D0.B8.D1.87.D0.B5.D1.81.D0.BA.D0.B8.D0.B5_.D0.B8_.D1.81.D0.B8.D0.BD.D1.82.D0.B0.D0.BA.D1.81.D0.B8.D1.87.D0.B5.D1.81.D0.BA.D0.B8.D0.B5_.D1.81.D0.B2.D0.BE.D0.B9.D1.81.D1.82.D0.B2.D0.B0"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Морфологические_и_синтаксические_свойства"></span></h3>
<p><b><a href = vnd.unilang:you.html>you</a></b>
</p><p><a href = vnd.unilang:личный.html>Ли́чное</a> местоимение <a href = vnd.unilang:второй.html>второ́го</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:лицо.html>лица</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:единственный.html>еди́нственного</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:и.html>и</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:множественный.html>мно́жественного</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:число.html>числа</a>. <a href = vnd.unilang:соответствующий.html>Соотве́тствующее</a> притяжательное местоимение — <a href = vnd.unilang:your.html>your</a>. <a href = vnd.unilang:косвенный.html>Ко́свенный</a> <a href = vnd.unilang:падеж.html>паде́ж</a> - <i><a href = vnd.unilang:you.html>you</a></i>.
</p>
